{"tid":166074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十七歲少年洪水橋墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-03-21T23:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T14:47:32.000Z","uid":79353,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"363e9516a961dc60d512261e6455d39194829a36","tid":166074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"今日（3月21日）晚上，元朗洪水橋有一名少年從高處墮下，送院後證實不治。 事件發生於晚上11時許，一名17歲少年被發現從洪福邨洪塱樓高處墮下，倒臥在行人通道上。救護員到場之後，隨即將男子送院，惟搶救無效。 警方正封鎖現場，調查墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-22-2017/36730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-22-2017%2F36730&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c3bcf98f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-22-2017/36730</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"1d7fec13336a3a6b0b49ddfaabe52eb54694997f","tid":166074,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae7f1af0dc0b4094154357b37a3735190b545b9d","tid":166074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福氣來架👍，一諗到係香港死做爛做買唔到一層300呎樓，一份人工養唔起冚家😅，喂！福氣來架👍<br />\n<br />\n港喱廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/171138_0e38f2989bcff71aeeb92a8d6399e905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F171138_0e38f2989bcff71aeeb92a8d6399e905.jpg&h=2755b6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我鄉下隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/583ti0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F583ti0i.jpg&h=c69a313e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港喱廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/u